Good news for our efforts to bring more #COVID19 vaccines to Europeans!

@EMA_News assessed that the @moderna_tx vaccine is safe &amp; effective.

Now we are working at full speed to approve it &amp; make it available in the EU.

@EMA_News Dear EMA social media team,
I very much appreciate updates via Twitter.
However, only a small minority of the users and even among journalists are familiar with the #CHMP and it's role. Maybe you consider some basic explanations?
